com.alprael.readwithoutme.model.entity

Class BooksRead

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.alprael.readwithoutme.model.entity.BooksRead

  • public class BooksRead
extends Object
    BooksRead entity for the Read Without Me database. This entity is the main connection between user and book. It takes in a book_id with a book_name, and a user_id with a display_name It does so only when the user has successfully read a book.
